io.customerly - package io.customerly
 
isLastSupportConversationAvailable() - Method in class io.customerly.Customerly
Call this method to indicate if from a previous Customerly.update(Callback.Success, Callback.Failure), Customerly.registerUser(String, String, String, Callback.Success, Callback.Failure) or Customerly.setAttributes(JSONObject, Callback.Success, Callback.Failure) an unread message is available.
isSurveyAvailable() - Method in class io.customerly.Customerly
Call this method to indicate if from a previous Customerly.update(Callback.Success, Callback.Failure), Customerly.registerUser(String, String, String, Callback.Success, Callback.Failure) or Customerly.setAttributes(JSONObject, Callback.Success, Callback.Failure) a survey is available.
